dcterms:creator: Constantine A. Balanis
dcterms:description: The RF GPS L1 passive patch antenna operates at the GPS L1 frequency of 1.57542 GHz and is designed for automotive applications. It has a radiating element size of 12.25 x 12.25 mm and is constructed on a ceramic/porcelain substrate.
dcterms:title: RF GPS L1 Passive Patch Antenna

dcterms:creator: Fawwaz T. Ulaby
dcterms:description: The Active GPS/GLONASS patch antenna operates at a frequency range of 1.575 to 1.610 GHz, with a center frequency of 1.5925 GHz. It is designed for automotive applications and has a similar radiating element size of 12.25 x 12.25 mm.
dcterms:title: Active GPS/GLONASS Patch Antenna
